# Docs/math/paste-ready-archive/

Paste-ready snippets that were prepared for direct inclusion in CHANGELOG,
CODE_MANUAL, or TOE-FACT-SHEET, retained here as historical archive
after the content was integrated.

These files do not carry independent canonical authority — they were
intermediate artifacts produced during autonomous research rounds. The
canonical pillar-status source is `Docs/status/TOE-FACT-SHEET.md` and
the individual `Docs/math/TECT-Math<NN>-*.tex.txt` theorem notes.

This directory is created per the 2026-04-24 Math82 repo cleanup
(Phase A relocation of root-level orphan PASTE-READY-* and
CHANGELOG-Pillar* files).
